    </div>
    <div class="sense-top-quote-wrapper">
      <blockquote class="sense-top-quote animation-init">
        <div class="inner">
          <p class="text">
            잘 고른<br>향수 하나,<br>
            <strong class="colored">열 옷</strong><br>
            <strong class="colored">안 부럽죠.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="from"><b class="name">전병배</b> 향료 마스터</p>
